name: SLC25A15
list.name: UKBB_20002_1482
Phenotype_description: Non-cancer illness code, self-reported: chronic fatigue syndrome
Phenotype_notes: Code for non-cancer illness. If the participant was uncertain of the type of illness they had had, then they described it to the interviewer (a trained nurse) who attempted to place it within the coding tree. If the illness could not be located in the coding tree then the interviewer entered a free-text description of it. These free-text descriptions were subsequently examined by a doctor and, where possible, matched to entries in the coding tree. Free-text descriptions which could not be matched with very high probability have been marked as \unclassifiable\.
